doc.field: A topographical map of the peninsula of Cape May with the country westward to Maurice River ; from original surveys and levelings, excepting the shore-lines of bays and beaches from Cape May Court House southward which are from the plane-table sheets of the U.S. Coast and Geodetic Survey ; based on the triangulation of the U.S. Coast and Geodetic Survey /
